sequenceDiagram
    participant Camera
    participant Capture
    participant Encoder
    participant Track as Video Track
    participant PC as Peer Connection
    participant Console

    loop Every Frame (30 FPS)
        Camera->>Capture: Raw frame (YUV)
        Capture->>Capture: Add timestamp
        Capture->>Encoder: Frame + metadata
        Encoder->>Encoder: H.264 encode
        Encoder->>Track: NAL units
        Track->>PC: RTP packetize
        PC->>Console: SRTP encrypted
    end

    Note over Console,PC: RTCP Feedback Loop
    Console-->>PC: RTCP receiver report
    PC-->>Encoder: Bitrate adjustment
